text: Tove Enblom (born 20 November 1994) is a Swedish footballer who plays Umeå IK in the Elitettan, a Swedish women league, as a goalkeeper. Enblom played for Djurgårdens IF Dam from 2012 to 2013, where she played 27 games. Enblom played for Umeå IK. Enblom is as of 2018 holdning the position as first goalkeeper in IFK Kalmar. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Swedish women's footballers Category:Living people Category:Djurgårdens IF Fotboll (women) players Category:Umeå IK players Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:IFK Kalmar players Category:Women's association football goalkeepers
